    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Manipulating the fabric of reality has become a mundane thing to you, but the more you do it, the more strain it puts on your body, leaving \"pieces\" of yourself behind as you travel.</p><p>When you reach 7th level, once per turn, you can gain additional uses of your <strong>Alternate Fates</strong> Yoru Clan Feature by spending a Hit Die as a Bonus Action.</p><p>When you reach 15th level, you are able to perform this as a Free Action on your turn.</p>",
